"        PA mean pressure (mmHg)",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        48 &plusmn; 12",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        27 &plusmn; 8*",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        24 &plusmn; 10",
